{"blogid": "122815157", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "49", "writerCollect": "7", "writerComment": "1", "writerFan": "2", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "494", "writerName": "一只猪咪", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_122815157.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "134790", "writerRankWeekly": "433157", "writerThumb": "2", "writerVisitNum": "13693", "blog_read_count": "1342", "blog_time": "于 2022-02-07 22:01:10 发布", "blog_title": "Rust语言——cargo", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p>cargo是rustup安装后自带的，cargo简单来说就是rust下的包管理工具</p>\n<p>以下是cargo的主要命令</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"170\" src=\"image\\0b358dbce23b469ea2b6888914bfbbf4.png\" width=\"710\"/></p>\n<p>首先在cmd中使用cargo语句cargo new hello_cargo来生成一个cargo项目(cargo项目可以实现大型的代码任务)，以下为cargo结构：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"439\" src=\"image\\f77e96622c884aa6bd6c0ad34941b3f2.png\" width=\"629\"/></p>\n<p>cargo.toml为该cargo文件的配置文件</p>\n<p>随后在cmd中输入命令:cd hello_cargo 进入hello_cargo的cargo文件</p>\n<p>而后输入命令:code . 在vscode中打开cargo文件</p>\n<p>最后对主函数进行编译输出 cmd命令为:cargo run 输出结果。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"261\" src=\"image\\58c816d4525c4fc5bb918a26ce7b04e5.png\" width=\"628\"/></p>\n<p>cargo check：检查代码，确保能通过编译，但不产生执行文件其速度比cargo build快得多</p>\n<p>编写代码时可以反复的使用cargo check检查代码，提高效率。</p>\n<p>cargo build --release 为发布构建</p>\n<p><strong>尽量使用cargo(功能强大，简化步骤)</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}